    "Details": "An upgrade to the 3032 model Orestes, the Orestes II swaps the 105 rated fusion engine for an XL version, The freed weight allowed TDF designers to add Artemis IV to the paired LRM-5s and double the allotted Machine Gun ammo.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar biomes.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 10/15 hexes / 300/450 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>        75     10\n<b>Left</b>          55     10\n<b>Right</b>        55     10\n<b>Rear</b>         45     10\n\n<b>Total</b>      240     50</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Missile Jammer</color>",
